# Vision

This project is for building a marketing-friendly blog/CMS system.

The system should:
- Be easy for marketing to use without developer support
- Support clean, consistent article formatting
- Allow internal linking to products and categories
- Be scalable for SEO-driven content
- Prevent users from breaking layout or structure

Tone:
- Simple
- Practical
- Not overly technical

This should feel like a tool marketing owns, not engineering.
